- **Responsive Design**: Mobile-first approach with breakpoints for tablet and desktop
- **Menu Overlay**: Elegant full-screen navigation with brand messaging
- **Image Optimization**: Responsive image sets with multiple sizes for performance
- **Brand Consistency**: CSS variables ensure consistent color usage across all pages
- **Accessibility**: Semantic HTML structure and proper alt text for images

## Development

### Running the Project
```bash
npm start  # Starts development server on port 3004
npm run dev  # Alternative command (same as start)
```

### File Organization
- `/css` - Stylesheets (normalize, webflow base, custom Tiara styles)
- `/images` - All brand assets, photos, icons, and product images
- `/fonts` - Custom brand fonts (Houstiq, Inter)
- `/js` - JavaScript files (Webflow interactions)

### Important Notes
- The site uses CSS custom properties (variables) for brand colors defined in `:root`
- Team images are displayed in grayscale via CSS filter
- Product and service images are organized in dedicated subdirectories
- All pages share consistent header and footer components

